rulesMessage:
**Clan Rules**

**Rule 1** â€” Teleporting any random player or enemy player (even friends) to a gang/clan base is prohibited.
**Rule 2** â€” New recruits will not have access to the community base until they earn the Member role.
**Rule 3** â€” Every member must keep a record of their balance.
**Rule 4** â€” Self-griefing or teleporting enemies is betrayal and punishable.
**Rule 5** â€” Gang leaders cannot make alliances without permission.
**Rule 6** â€” Betrayal = blacklist + permanent ban (unless apology).
**Rule 7** â€” Sub leaders cannot kick/ban without reason and must inform leadership.
**Rule 8** â€” Infighting: the one who starts the fight is punished.
**Rule 9** â€” Everyone must be treated equally.
**Rule 10** â€” No trash talk toward teammates.
**Rule 11** â€” No team killing.
**Rule 12** â€” No yoinking shulkers.
**Rule 13** â€” No begging for teleports to private bases. Leaking coords = punishment.
**Rule 14** â€” Threatening to leak coords is not tolerated.
**Rule 15** â€” Dropping into ENVOYS without leader command = punishment.
**Rule 16** â€” Disrespecting leaders/members = 1-week suspension.
